No.

22
00:02:31.693 --> 00:02:37.407 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I have come to realize just how much you
reject the notion of killing other humans.

23
00:02:38.116 --> 00:02:40.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
We must work together.

24
00:02:41.077 --> 00:02:42.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yeah, right.

25
00:02:42.871 --> 00:02:48.293 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
