47
00:03:43.014 --> 00:03:46.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Well, supposing we just catch
the guy instead of offing him,

48
00:03:46.601 --> 00:03:48.186 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
