50
00:03:50.438 --> 00:03:51.356 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
He looks like this.

51
00:03:51.940 --> 00:03:54.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
