59
00:04:13.169 --> 00:04:14.045 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yeah.

60
00:04:14.128 --> 00:04:17.131 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
