70
00:04:45.410 --> 00:04:47.704 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But I actually did get hurt.

71
00:04:47.787 --> 00:04:49.622 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
This is real, isn't it? Isn't it?

72
00:04:50.290 --> 00:04:51.874 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Please calm down.

73
00:04:56.838 --> 00:04:59.507 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
