up to this point,

78
00:05:13.313 --> 00:05:14.564 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
but let's stop here.

79
00:05:14.647 --> 00:05:16.149 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Stop?

80
00:05:16.232 --> 00:05:18.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
