86
00:05:30.330 --> 00:05:31.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Oh, I know!

87
00:05:31.664 --> 00:05:32.874 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You said something

88
00:05:32.957 --> 00:05:36.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
about Izumi Shinichi's
right hand before, didn't you?

89
00:05:36.377 --> 00:05:37.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Did I?

90
00:05:37.462 --> 00:05:39.505 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You did! You definitely did!

91
00:05:39.589 --> 00:05:41.841 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I see it now! You knew it, too!

92
00:05:41.924 --> 00:05:42.759 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
That's right!

93
00:05:43.426 --> 00:05:45.678 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
