95
00:05:48.222 --> 00:05:50.475 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Please, tell me the truth!

96
00:05:50.558 --> 00:05:52.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
