98
00:05:54.270 --> 00:05:56.147 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You can't fool me!

99
00:06:05.364 --> 00:06:09.619 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
