<i>with human help.</i>

100
00:06:11.954 --> 00:06:14.707 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>In the end, little was accomplished.</i>

101
00:06:14.791 --> 00:06:17.168 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Should I get rid of</i>
<i>that private investigator?</i>

102
