108
00:07:33.161 --> 00:07:35.079 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Man, I'm exhausted.

109
00:07:35.663 --> 00:07:37.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Well, well. Making yourself comfortable?

110
00:07:38.082 --> 00:07:39.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Want some?

111
00:07:39.208 --> 00:07:40.334 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
