113
00:07:48.384 --> 00:07:50.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Are you wrapped up
in something dangerous lately?

114
00:07:50.678 --> 00:07:51.721 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
