125
00:08:23.419 --> 00:08:26.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You should know your place.

126
00:08:26.672 --> 00:08:29.592 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Know my place, huh?

127
00:08:29.675 --> 00:08:31.761 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yup, stay small.

128
00:08:32.470 --> 00:08:35.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'm your husband, for crying out loud.

129
00:08:35.723 --> 00:08:36.724 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
THE JAPANESE MYSTERY GENRE

130
00:08:36.807 --> 00:08:37.642 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
THE WESTERN MYSTERY GENRE
MYSTERY ANTHOLOGY

131
00:08:37.725 --> 00:08:39.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Just watch.</i>

132
00:08:40.019 --> 00:08:42.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I'm going to surprise everyone!</i>

133
00:08:44.440 --> 00:08:51.155 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
