137
00:09:00.873 --> 00:09:02.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Shinichi.

138
00:09:02.416 --> 00:09:03.876 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
They found him.

139
00:09:03.960 --> 00:09:04.835 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Okay.

140
00:09:04.919 --> 00:09:07.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
