144
00:09:26.691 --> 00:09:27.900 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Please get in.

145
00:09:30.987 --> 00:09:32.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
