149
00:09:41.706 --> 00:09:44.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>He doesn't have to be so terrified.</i>

150
00:09:49.255 --> 00:09:51.632 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
