215
00:12:59.945 --> 00:13:01.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Your client is a parasite.

216
00:13:01.906 --> 00:13:03.157 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Whâ€¦

217
00:13:03.240 --> 00:13:04.241 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
