222
00:13:16.253 --> 00:13:19.215 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
but perhaps your client's name
sounds like hers?

223
00:13:19.298 --> 00:13:21.175 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tamiya Ryouko.

224
00:13:21.258 --> 00:13:22.885 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tamura Reiko.

225
00:13:24.345 --> 00:13:29.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Yeah, we're pretty half-assed
when it comes to names.

226
00:13:29.225 --> 00:13:31.393 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
If you refuse to back down,

227
00:13:31.477 --> 00:13:34.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
