00:13:53.374 --> 00:13:54.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
after we figured it might be her.

234
00:13:55.334 --> 00:13:58.254 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
