235
00:13:58.337 --> 00:13:59.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
What's she trying to pull?

236
00:13:59.964 --> 00:14:04.051 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
